Players will not be happy unless they are the highest lvl possible.  That means they go where they can get the most exp, leading to overpopulated zones.  For these players, adding more lvls means going back to the same old boring experience camping.  Doing that post 50 is tedious enough.<br>
<br>
You can't lvl doing only raids.  It will not happen.  That leads to long boring experience camps, be it soloing or in a 6 man group. These are just going to get longer if they raids the exp curve again.</font><P><p align="center"><img
